org.cef.handler

类 CefLifeSpanHandlerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.handler.CefLifeSpanHandlerAdapter
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    CefLifeSpanHandler 

    public abstract class CefLifeSpanHandlerAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements CefLifeSpanHandler
    An abstract adapter class for receiving life span events. The methods in this class are empty. This class exists as convenience for creating handler objects. (用于接收生命周期事件的抽象适配器类。此类中的方法为空。此类的存在是为了方便创建处理程序对象。)

      • doClose

        public boolean doClose(CefBrowser browser)
        从接口复制的说明: CefLifeSpanHandler
        Called when a browser has received a request to close. If CEF created an OS window for the browser returning false will send an OS close notification to the browser window's top-level owner (e.g. WM_CLOSE on Windows, performClose: on OS-X and "delete_event" on Linux). If no OS window exists (window rendering disabled) returning false will cause the browser object to be destroyed immediately. Return true if the browser is parented to another window and that other window needs to receive close notification via some non-standard technique. (当浏览器收到关闭请求时调用。如果CEF为浏览器创建了OS窗口，则返回false将向浏览器窗口的顶级所有者发送OS关闭通知（例如，在Windows上为WM_CLOSE，在OS-X上为performClose ：，在Linux上为“ delete_event”）。如果不存在OS窗口（禁用窗口渲染），则返回false将立即破坏浏览器对象。如果浏览器是另一个窗口的父级，并且另一个窗口需要通过某种非标准技术接收关闭通知，则返回true。)
        指定者:
        doClose 在接口中  CefLifeSpanHandler
        参数:
        browser - The browser generating the event. (-浏览器生成事件。)
        返回:
        False to send an OS close notification to the browser window's top-level owner. (将操作系统关闭通知发送到浏览器窗口的顶级所有者为False。)

      • onBeforeClose

        public void onBeforeClose(CefBrowser browser)
        从接口复制的说明: CefLifeSpanHandler
        Called just before a browser is destroyed. Release all references to the browser object and do not attempt to execute any methods on the browser object after this callback returns. If this is a modal window and a custom modal loop implementation was provided in runModal() this callback should be used to exit the custom modal loop. See doClose() documentation for additional usage information. (在浏览器被销毁之前调用。释放所有对浏览器对象的引用，并且在此回调返回之后，不要尝试对浏览器对象执行任何方法。如果这是模态窗口，并且在runModal（）中提供了自定义模态循环实现，则应使用此回调退出自定义模态循环。有关其他用法信息，请参见doClose（）文档。)
        指定者:
        onBeforeClose 在接口中  CefLifeSpanHandler
        参数:
        browser - The browser generating the event. (-浏览器生成事件。)

      • onBeforePopup

        public boolean onBeforePopup(CefBrowser browser,
                             CefFrame frame,
                             java.lang.String target_url,
                             java.lang.String target_frame_name)
        从接口复制的说明: CefLifeSpanHandler
        Called on the IO thread before a new popup window is created. (在创建新的弹出窗口之前在IO线程上调用。)
        指定者:
        onBeforePopup 在接口中  CefLifeSpanHandler
        参数:
        browser - The source of the popup request. (-弹出请求的来源。)
        frame - The source of the popup request. Instance only valid within the scope of this method. (-弹出请求的来源。实例仅在此方法的范围内有效。)
        target_url - May be empty if none is specified with the request. (-如果请求中未指定任何内容，则可以为空。)
        target_frame_name - May be empty if none is specified with the request. (-如果请求中未指定任何内容，则可以为空。)
        返回:
        True to cancel creation of the popup window or false to proceed. (如果为True，则取消创建弹出窗口；如果为false，则继续进行。)
